      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TAYLOR MADE BLUE (8) resumed from a break finishing fourth (19.51) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Will be much improved. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. DESI'S DREAM (2) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and five placings from 12 starts. Was out of the placings last time (21.35) at Nowra in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 4 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. BEST OF SALLY (1) was in the minors two back (20.00) at this track but ran below best last time at Richmond, finishing 6th. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. PRECURSOR (7) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
